{"tid":934376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張達明：三本護照短時簽發　且用舊護照入境　孟晚舟是同時有三本","createTime":"2018-12-09T08:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T23:05:37.000Z","uid":47714,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b812337fc16e2082ba28cd658855e6b7c123bf","tid":934376,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tmcheungeric/photos/a.859301934112981/2139829602726868/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTmcheungeric%2Fphotos%2Fa.859301934112981%2F2139829602726868%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2FCoEWZ1oSvMNVxao%2BLpiVlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=dbd3e124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Tmcheungeric/photos/a.859301934112981/2139829602726868/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：張達明（法律學者）<br />\n<br />\n註：看到一些評論，認為孟晚舟擁有三本不同號碼的特區護照不足為奇，因為在續領或補領特區護照時，護照號碼都會改變，她可能「坐飛機多過坐巴士」，所以舊護照蓋滿章後便需要換領。<br />\n<br />\n作出這些評論的人可能沒有留意當中關鍵細節，就是三本護照都是K J字頭，表示三本護照是在一段短時期內簽發，這麼快便蓋滿章的機會不高（特別是現在很多國家出入境也不再需要在護照上蓋章）。更重要的是，入境處資料顯示，護照持有人在領取新護照時，必須將舊護照交回入境處註銷，但根據美國司法部呈交的資料 (<a href=\"https://zh.scribd.com/document/395185754/Surrey-RCMP-Const-Winston-Yep-s-affidavit#fullscreen&amp;from_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F395185754%2FSurrey-RCMP-Const-Winston-Yep-s-affidavit%23fullscreen%26from_embed&d=%2FCoEWZ1oSvMNVxao%2BLpiVlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4460c7ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.scribd.com/document/395185754/Surrey-RCMP-Const-Winston-Yep-s-affidavit#fullscreen&amp;from_embed</a>, at p 11)，她這次是用第二本護照(即KJ0403962)入境加拿大，而並非用最新簽發的第三本護照(即KJ0479108)，這表示她在未有註銷第二本護照的情況下獲簽發第三本護照。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我仍然認為香港政府需要盡快徹查事件及作出公開解釋。<br />\n<br />\n__________<br />\n根據美國司法部呈交的文件(<a href=\"https://zh.scribd.com/document/395185756/Letter-from-the-U-S-Justice-Department\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F395185756%2FLetter-from-the-U-S-Justice-Department&d=%2FCoEWZ1oSvMNVxao%2BLpiVlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=bb0dba3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.scribd.com/document/395185756/Letter-from-the-U-S-Justice-Department</a>)，孟晚舟居然擁有由香港政府發出的三本不同號碼的護照，為避免世界各國懷疑香港特區護照的可靠性，影響香港市民的利益，香港政府需要盡快徹查事件及作出公開解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/fYBgQ8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfYBgQ8&h=25bedc8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba84612f564c6f534c865b01fb7e5f4797882934","tid":934376,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6019156496e516060c0e60f38a91a1e58cf003b6","tid":934376,"uid":10929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"要不是香港畀護照你地中國人，真係唔洗指意出國"},{"pid":"c6333f46de7b8174adfdf422b286c2ff1af3c1ec","tid":934376,"uid":26329,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6019156496e516060c0e60f38a91a1e58cf003b6","tid":934376,"uid":10929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"要不是香港畀護照你地中國人，真係唔洗指意出國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"好快香港護照都出唔到國"},{"pid":"bd9dbb5df85eba91c9320d55d60d67416836c586","tid":934376,"uid":61675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"共產黨唔玩死香港唔心息"},{"pid":"ed8533712175fba385d0f132a4d3fe47ed97b159","tid":934376,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"而家話三本香港護照嘅美國出入境紀錄完全一樣"},{"pid":"2a5712a2dc909f15117ed21c5241d7bbf8414038","tid":934376,"uid":136735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"一個好好既香港你唔去學習唔去保護<br />\n只識諗閪野利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82b75ce57a7a426797170338d1edcda3438f263","tid":934376,"uid":6293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"政府咁耐都冇出聲即係佢冇講錯啦<img src=\"/as